r />\n<br />\n另外如有footage 拍50p<br />\nexport 25p 會唔會帶問題？"},{"pid":"3fd0d57fd1c052b4d77f5c8a6dcdeb4d185179ba","tid":26321,"uid":6587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知 片25格<br />\n用pr sequence開25格<br />\nexport24格<br />\n結果會會係 數字上岩格 實際上唔岩格定會點<br />\n<br />\n另外如有footage 拍50p<br />\nexport 25p 會唔會帶問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經我問過類似問題....."},{"pid":"25891c845fb95966e612ac6f4871b74b8f8593cc","tid":26321,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想知 片25格<br />\n用pr sequence開25格<br />\nexport24格<br />\n結果會會係 數字上岩格 實際上唔岩格定會點<br />\n<br />\n另外如有footage 拍50p<br />\nexport 25p 會唔會帶問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曾經我問過類似問題.....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPr會幫你resample, 所以影響不大<br />\n不過time interpolation有三個mode揀，optical flow會最靚"},{"pid":"f9efb18693ca9fa523dcd2ec5bc00c2077aebc9e","tid":26321,"uid":27612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T20:53:34.000Z","msg":"新手想開拍片，應該要由咩開始學？"},{"pid":"842b02512a86172804ef0f1d44b181eecf7d2d33","tid":26321,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:00:27.000Z","msg":"有無唔洗穩定器既movement技巧分享？"},{"pid":"e5205c5da94bb49fa5635960f5197bc6929a63be","tid":26321,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T21:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新手想開拍片，應該要由咩開始學？</blockquote><br />\n度分鏡<br />\n度storyboard"},{"pid":"db19240d9bb7b42c1444e10b5c18b69bd3a2f6ec","tid":26321,"uid":27612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T22:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新手想開拍片，應該要由咩開始學？</blockquote><br />\n度分鏡<br />\n度storyboard</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇blog或者網或者youtube或者書可以介紹下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前讀書時上堂做功課都係亂黎，是但拍啲野，然後話自己拍紀錄片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaf07717f613a778085