要咪嘴既shot多數25fps"},{"pid":"1530a4a9453dbb9e6c11eae499af76b9e7060c31","tid":26321,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T09:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無唔洗穩定器既movement技巧分享？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n身郁 instead of 手郁，試下將部機慢慢細幅度咁打八字再掟下fo咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520abef055c8f6e6fd3bbedecccb5727b605a648","tid":26321,"uid":38128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問 依家拍片都係咪拍50fps or 60fps，方便後期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n視乎個shot既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有對白/要咪嘴既shot多數25fps</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問點解我拍60 放落30格既timeline 係正常既"},{"pid":"73723b8a47995f15db8924982b51a3355a3ef7cf","tid":26321,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問 依家拍片都係咪拍50fps or 60fps，方便後期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n視乎個shot既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有對白/要咪嘴既shot多數25fps</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問點解我拍60 放落30格既timeline 係正常既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你slow down佢就會見到個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f932fdb24935321f788b104ac970fbc505784d","tid":26321,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n視乎個shot既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有對白/要咪嘴既shot多數25fps</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問點解我拍60 放落30格既timeline 係正常既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你slow down佢就會見到個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係用ARRI/RED嗰d 拍左50/60fps playback都會係正常速度"},{"pid":"5722fcc3933da14cedb60d7cce09a7e00d6c94c5","tid":26321,"uid":38128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T13:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n請問點解我拍60 放落30格既timeline 係正常既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你slow down佢就會見到個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係用ARRI/RED嗰d 拍左50/60fps playback都會係正常速度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以點解唔直接拍60,要聲要正常既又得，想slow down又得？"},{"pid":"74d6af6a2798c1362d2cf4a9c5452b3ef78a1b1e","tid":26321,"uid":39907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你slow down佢就會見到個分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係用ARRI/RED嗰d 拍左50/60fps playback都會係正常速度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以點解唔直接拍60,要聲要正常既又得，想slow down又得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你拍60同30個shutter angle都唔同啦，個look係有唔同，例如慢shutter既blur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋個scene唔一定夠光拍60"},{"pid":"8482de18874ab0525234a45ab26ecdc9fe71ec27","tid":26321,"uid":15298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"分享下同人拍嘅片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HFGV6-u-EME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHFGV6-u-EME&d=XgJxA7mL2pmn53RU8UFtOpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3a1bb472\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HFGV6-u-EME</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位畀啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}